								README


Initial Setup
/-------------------------------------------------------/
Install python-pip (command apt-get install python-pip)
Install python-lxml (command apt-get install python-lxml)
The program expects the medsamp2012.xml document to be imported into baseX. The database name for the document must be medsamp2012.
The program expects the acm-turing-awards.xml document to be imported into eXistDB. The collection name for the document must be acm-turing-awards.

Command to start baseX server
/------------------------------------/
cd /opt/basex/bin
sudo ./basexhttp

Command to stat eXistDB server
/------------------------------------/
cd /opt/eXistDB/bin
sudo ./startup.sh

Instructions to access and search bib library
/-------------------------------------------/
1. Install required modules
2. Start up baseX and eXistDB servers
3. Open broswer and go to http://localhost/~coursework/cgi-bin/bibfinder.cgi
4. Select search criteria
5. Hit Submit  
6. If a bibilography is matched, it will be deplayed in the query results section.
7. If no bibilography is found, NONE will be printed out in the query section.

